<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="opposition-n">opposition <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌɒpə'zɪʃn/    美 /ˌɑːpə'zɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>反对；相反；敌对：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There was a great deal of <strong>opposition to</strong> the decision.
对这个决定有很多反对意见。</p></div></div>